WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.829
Well, good evening family.

00:00:01.829 --> 00:00:04.343
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:04.343 --> 00:00:13.293
We're going to pray and go over some of the things that have happened in the news in the last 48 hours or so.

00:00:13.293 --> 00:00:14.920
It's been a good weekend.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:16.544
I pray you've had a wonderful weekend.

00:00:16.544 --> 00:00:17.960
The weather's been nice.

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:23.320
We've gotten some rain, and so, giving Jesus all the glory for the rain.

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:24.280
Isn't it wonderful?

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:28.720
Things start to get really green whenever the rain comes.

00:00:28.720 --> 00:00:30.280
I love it.

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:33.400
The flowers, everything—the animals love it.

00:00:33.400 --> 00:00:35.755
Everything gets happy for the rain.

00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:39.410
Father, we thank you for all the rain that we've had.

00:00:39.410 --> 00:00:42.735
Thank you for all the rain we have in the forecast this week.

00:00:42.735 --> 00:00:46.320
We're so grateful for all the rain that you've given us.

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:49.769
And I thank you that it's going to rain from sea to shining sea.

00:00:50.820 --> 00:00:52.670
We call in the rain.

00:00:52.670 --> 00:00:58.187
We thank you, Lord, that the drought is broken in the name of Jesus.

00:00:58.187 --> 00:01:05.600
We call it in again this week already; we call it in from the north, the south, east, and the west.

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:13.720
We thank you, Lord, that the rain is coming on the jet stream as the low-pressure system is bringing it forth.

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:19.180
But not only that, Father, we thank you, Lord, that it stalls out and just keeps dumping on our area.

00:01:19.180 --> 00:01:27.720
I thank you, Lord, that we would have enough to fill up our lakes, our ponds, our streams, our rivers, and Father, our reservoirs.

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:35.120
Father, we thank you, Lord, that we have at least five inches this week in Jesus' name to get out of the deficit.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:36.491
Everybody say amen on that.

00:01:36.491 --> 00:01:41.800
You agree for your area because you don't just stop whenever you just get a little bit.

00:01:41.800 --> 00:01:47.760
That's the beginning; whenever you make it a greasy spot, you keep praying and calling the rain in in the spring.

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:51.648
Well, Brandon, isn't it supposed to rain in the spring?

00:01:51.648 --> 00:01:56.920
Yes, but we had a major drought and we have to catch up.

00:01:56.920 --> 00:02:12.400
And so, for those of you who are having a lot of rain, don't take it for granted because fires are terrible when everything's burning up and you go, 'Man, we've got to have rain quick.

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:12.987
' All right.

00:02:12.987 --> 00:02:17.032
So, okay, we have a lot of news here, Braden.

00:02:18.636 --> 00:02:20.289
This is where I'm at with...

00:02:20.564 --> 00:02:22.680
that's the chat.

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:26.390
I don't want to see it.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:32.040
It moves in my eye whenever I see all those people talking.

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:39.200
I want to say this.

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:41.930
Oh, so we see the Sooners come out.

00:02:41.930 --> 00:02:48.533
Do you remember when I told you Japan will be the Sooner concerning crypto?

00:02:48.533 --> 00:02:55.720
Japan, South Korea—I said they will be the ones that implement things before America.

00:02:55.720 --> 00:03:07.260
And you'll start to see Japan implement the crypto laws and really try to go after it like America will in the days ahead.

00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:09.089
But I called them the Sooners.

00:03:09.089 --> 00:03:11.853
And I said, 'I saw the Boomer Schooner wagon.

00:03:11.853 --> 00:03:19.125
' If you're familiar with OU college football, they have a Schooner wagon.

00:03:19.125 --> 00:03:25.519
Well, every time they make a touchdown, they run out that wagon and celebrate the touchdown.

00:03:25.519 --> 00:03:28.000
And I said, 'This is what you're about to see.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:34.360
' I said, 'I saw Sooners coming across Japan and South Korea in the days ahead.

00:03:34.360 --> 00:03:39.098
' So Braden said, 'Daddy, the word is coming to pass.

00:03:39.098 --> 00:03:40.040
' Do you see it?

00:03:40.040 --> 00:03:41.080
Yeah.

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:43.366
Is something wrong?

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:47.320
Right.

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:55.420
Okay.

00:03:55.420 --> 00:04:01.640
See this article right here?

00:04:07.165 --> 00:04:07.830
I don't know—some of this stuff, you have to be careful.

00:04:07.830 --> 00:04:12.783
There are a lot of scammers, but this is a good one.

00:04:12.783 --> 00:04:20.693
Braden says, 'Okay, Japan officially approves bill to recognize cryptocurrency as a financial asset.

00:04:20.693 --> 00:04:21.306
' The Sooners.

00:04:21.306 --> 00:04:21.920
Ain't that neat?

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:25.049
I thought that was so cool.

00:04:42.351 --> 00:04:42.582
I said, 'Look, Lord, it's happening.

00:04:42.582 --> 00:04:47.307
' Just like you said, Japan is announcing their recognition of cryptocurrency.

00:04:47.307 --> 00:04:48.845
The Sooners are at work.

00:04:48.845 --> 00:04:50.130
They're sending out the wagon.

00:04:50.130 --> 00:04:50.950
Here we go.

00:04:50.950 --> 00:04:59.630
Then we have the little gray-headed guy saying about America and Coinbase coming out and saying it's time to get it done.

00:04:59.630 --> 00:05:01.920
Do you have that?

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:02.347
No.

00:05:02.347 --> 00:05:03.200
Oh, you don't?

00:05:03.200 --> 00:05:03.640
Okay.

00:05:03.640 --> 00:05:05.149
Do you have anything about...

00:05:05.149 --> 00:05:07.744
well, I thought that's what we were talking about.

00:05:07.744 --> 00:05:08.800
I'm sorry.

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:18.120
I've been exercising.

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:20.120
I've been out trying to do walks.

00:05:37.620 --> 00:05:44.347
So, I haven't had time to talk to Braden before it got dark because I'm trying to get this weight down as quickly as possible.

00:05:44.347 --> 00:05:51.650
I've gotten 25 going on 30 lbs off and I'm giving God all the glory for it.

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:54.293
You know, the older I get, it seems...

00:05:54.293 --> 00:06:08.310
when I was in my 20s, it fell off a lot faster, but now I have to work harder, it seems.

00:06:08.310 --> 00:06:10.360
But that's all right.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:18.320
We're going to get it off.

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:28.653
And I told Diana, I said, 'You know, just watching your calories and exercising.

00:06:28.653 --> 00:06:31.747
' I've been walking, taking walks, and it's fun, I guess.

00:06:31.747 --> 00:06:32.209
Woohoo!

00:06:32.209 --> 00:06:33.491
But Paisley likes it.

00:06:33.491 --> 00:06:36.187
All right, here is the guy that's over Coinbase.

00:06:36.187 --> 00:06:37.067
We agree.

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:52.840
So Scott—this SEC Scott—he said they want to get the Clarity Act done.

00:06:52.840 --> 00:06:56.680
Basically, he's making an announcement saying, 'We've got to get this Clarity Act done.

00:07:09.400 --> 00:07:10.480
You all have to stop delaying.

00:07:10.480 --> 00:07:15.771
' And then the guy that's over Coinbase is saying, 'We agree.

00:07:15.771 --> 00:07:21.195
We agree it's time to pass the Clarity Act.

00:07:21.195 --> 00:07:23.409
' So the Sooner is before this.

00:07:28.616 --> 00:07:28.868
The Treasury Secretary...

00:07:28.868 --> 00:07:35.560
Congress has spent the better part of half a decade trying to pass a framework to onshore the future of finance.

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:42.945
And so I said, 'What are we going to see in the days ahead?

00:07:43.845 --> 00:07:44.070
A Clarity Act.

00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:46.880
' That's what we're going to pray about.

00:07:46.880 --> 00:08:02.870
We keep praying about it and I said I saw the boys—Donald Trump's sons—with the coins and they were dancing and they were going into the new building.

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:11.493
They had a big building and I said I saw the building start growing and it doubled the building that they had.

00:08:11.493 --> 00:08:20.785
So when you're looking into a vision, I don't try to add to or take away from anything, but what is it talking about?

00:08:20.785 --> 00:08:22.760
Was that building their real estate empire?

00:08:29.420 --> 00:08:32.410
I tried to figure out what the Lord's trying to say without being flaky about it.

00:08:32.410 --> 00:08:50.691
But when I saw that building standing there and it was all the Trump letters, and then I saw this new tower start to grow and it had digital all in it, and it started to make the real estate building where they are at now look really small compared to what they're about to do.

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:53.880
And Barron came on the scene.

00:08:53.880 --> 00:09:06.600
Now I don't know how far Barron has left school, if he's going to college or whatever, but I'm sure he is.

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:12.500
And if he's getting a Master's or whatever, who knows?

00:09:12.500 --> 00:09:21.080
But I know that I saw Barron come into the building and all of a sudden Barron made the whole building start having digital writing on it.

00:09:21.390 --> 00:09:25.160
And I saw Eric leading them in.

00:09:25.160 --> 00:09:28.060
But Barron was the mastermind.

00:09:28.060 --> 00:09:32.107
His mind was the one that was running this thing more.

00:09:32.107 --> 00:09:36.630
Eric went and then all of a sudden the building started to come alive.

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:55.315
If everybody remembers that vision that I had about a week ago, I just get excited about it when they start talking this stuff because I'm believing God for a financial turnaround for the body of Christ, for the wealth of the sinners laid up for the righteous.

00:09:56.940 --> 00:10:01.120
And I believe in the name of Jesus, we're going to see it sooner than later.

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:04.071
I keep standing on it.

00:10:04.071 --> 00:10:05.711
I'm not letting it go.

00:10:05.711 --> 00:10:23.945
As we hear everybody talk about the markets crashing and things looking bad—'Oh no, the sky is falling, Chicken Little'—I believe that as for me and my house, we're going to be blessed and we're going to keep standing, regardless if the Great Depression is going all around us and we have a major 1929-style crash.

00:10:23.945 --> 00:10:31.320
I remember a preacher talking and he said, 'During the Great Depression, my mom and daddy never went without anything.

00:10:31.320 --> 00:10:35.320
' He said, 'They always tithed.

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:36.806
They always gave.

00:10:36.806 --> 00:10:39.234
They always sowed to the church.

00:10:39.234 --> 00:10:44.093
And God always took care of them during the Great Depression.

00:10:44.093 --> 00:10:46.107
They never lacked anything.

00:10:46.107 --> 00:10:48.848
They always made their house payment.

00:10:48.848 --> 00:10:52.480
They always had food on the table for us kids.

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:55.160
They always had all this.

00:10:55.160 --> 00:11:00.520
' And he was talking about how God always provided even in the Great Depression.

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:05.663
Now, if you're talking about my granny who was 106 when she went home to be with the Lord, they struggled.

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:14.440
They didn't believe in tithing.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:15.311
They didn't believe in giving.

00:11:15.311 --> 00:11:17.555
I don't even think they were really good Baptists.

00:11:17.555 --> 00:11:21.080
They were Baptist, but I don't even think they were really good Baptists.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:24.510
They were just kind of lukewarm Baptists even at that.

00:11:25.460 --> 00:11:31.260
She said, "Brendon, we had to eat black crow, you know, the big black crows flying around in the sky.

00:11:32.978 --> 00:11:46.095
" She goes, "Daddy would go out there and shoot those black crows and we would eat crow pie, blackbird pie, black crow pie, and we would try to make it out of whatever we had to.

00:11:46.095 --> 00:11:52.120
" Then she goes, "And if those became scarce because people were killing all the crows off, we started eating possum.

00:11:53.450 --> 00:11:58.752
" She said, "We'd go down in the creek beds and look for possums and we'd start eating possum.

00:12:08.114 --> 00:12:08.331
" I said, "Granny, what did possum taste like?

00:12:08.331 --> 00:12:11.326
" She said, "It tastes like gristly, really fatty.

00:12:28.577 --> 00:12:29.034
It was real oily because the possum was real greasy.

00:12:36.171 --> 00:12:36.623
" She said, "We used to try to fry it because we were starving.

00:12:36.623 --> 00:12:53.220
" She goes, "And I'll never forget getting those flour sacks from the feed store and Mama couldn't give us good clothes and we were growing as kids, so she would always make us feed store sack clothes.

00:12:53.220 --> 00:13:03.975
" Even up until Granny went home to be with the Lord at 106, she would always go out in the ditch and find stuff to eat.

00:13:03.975 --> 00:13:09.648
She'd go out there and all kinds of poke greens and lamb's quarter, whatever she could find.

00:13:09.648 --> 00:13:24.960
She'd go out there and start digging in the yard and pull it up by the roots and she would cook it and eat it, and it stunk so bad.

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:27.347
But she was healthy.

00:13:27.347 --> 00:13:30.680
She lived to be 106 years old.

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:44.520
The only reason she went home was she fell and hurt her hip and they were going to put her in the nursing home and she willed herself to death.

00:13:44.520 --> 00:13:47.931
She said, "I'm not going to the nursing home.

00:13:47.931 --> 00:14:01.253
" She gave up the ghost right there on the bed because she was determined not to go to the nursing home.

00:14:01.253 --> 00:14:05.460
She did not want to go or she'd probably still be here.

00:14:05.460 --> 00:14:07.000
She is a fighter.

00:14:07.000 --> 00:14:09.126
She wanted to live.

00:14:09.126 --> 00:14:14.040
But she didn't want to go to the nursing home and she was alive.

00:14:14.040 --> 00:14:17.300
She wanted to take care of herself.

00:14:17.300 --> 00:14:23.280
Even until then, to make a long story short, she took sponge baths.

00:14:23.280 --> 00:14:28.620
Didn't have to; had money, but she wouldn't even take a bath in the shower.

00:14:28.620 --> 00:14:48.010
She would fill a pan up full of water and dip the sponge and take a sponge bath and wash her hair because she was so scared of not having, and she saved foil.

00:14:48.010 --> 00:14:49.366
She saved everything.

00:14:53.693 --> 00:14:53.951
But my point is that generation knew how to live off the land.

00:14:53.951 --> 00:14:55.240
They had some grit.

00:14:55.240 --> 00:14:58.880
Granny and them had some grit.

00:14:58.880 --> 00:15:04.790
She made the best buttermilk biscuits I ever had in my life.

00:15:19.994 --> 00:15:20.297
But I'm going to tell you that 10-year window for the Great Depression affected her for the rest of her life for decades to come.

00:15:20.297 --> 00:15:25.886
That financial lack that hit America shook her for decades and decades.

00:15:28.840 --> 00:15:29.360
And that was when she was just a young girl.

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:35.377
That tells you how we're so blessed; our generation is so blessed.

00:15:35.377 --> 00:15:38.750
We've never tasted that kind of stuff.

00:15:38.750 --> 00:15:40.260
That was only 100 years ago.

00:15:40.260 --> 00:15:44.925
1929 will be 100 years in the next couple of years.

00:15:44.925 --> 00:15:52.631
I'm not trying to say all that to freak you out.

00:15:52.631 --> 00:15:57.440
I've seen it again and again.

00:16:03.240 --> 00:16:03.673
And that's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:16:03.673 --> 00:16:11.680
If we are the body of Christ, we must learn how to give.

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:17.070
We must learn how to trust God for a great shaking to awaken.

00:16:17.070 --> 00:16:20.130
Do I believe we're going to see 1929?

00:16:25.650 --> 00:16:25.960
I pray with all my heart we don't.

00:16:25.960 --> 00:16:28.274
But history seems to repeat itself.

00:16:28.274 --> 00:16:29.900
People are asleep.

00:16:45.575 --> 00:16:46.193
What is the mechanism to the revival?

00:16:46.193 --> 00:16:49.771
What brings what we're looking for?

00:16:49.771 --> 00:16:51.200
What is the first domino?

00:16:52.173 --> 00:16:55.710
It seems that America is stiff-necked and God's going to get their attention somehow.

00:17:11.064 --> 00:17:14.369
I just think it's interesting to me.

00:17:14.369 --> 00:17:23.664
As I pray into all this stuff and as we see this, what did I tell you we would see?

00:17:23.664 --> 00:17:32.983
What the Holy Spirit warned us about President Trump, the war, and all the things.

00:17:32.983 --> 00:17:40.514
I said when the tariffs don't go into effect and we don't pray the Supreme Court justice to coincide with him, we're in the valley of decision.

00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:48.000
This was back in January.

00:17:59.100 --> 00:17:59.390
I said this will be a major turning point of his presidency.

00:18:11.560 --> 00:18:12.020
And I said the next phase will be war, war, war.

00:18:19.148 --> 00:18:19.360
I said Trump will be known as a wartime president.

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:24.296
When he first started, I told you this over a year ago.

00:18:24.296 --> 00:18:31.710
He came out saying, "I'm full of peace.

00:18:36.040 --> 00:18:36.232
I want peace.

00:18:36.232 --> 00:18:44.564
" But God will use him to shake the nations.

00:18:44.564 --> 00:18:49.800
He will crack his whip and he will shake the nations in making America great again.

00:18:49.800 --> 00:18:56.780
There will be a business side of him that we've never seen before.

00:18:56.780 --> 00:18:58.560
All gloves are off.

00:18:58.560 --> 00:18:59.120
Why?

00:18:59.120 --> 00:19:02.795
Because he's not going to be president again.

00:19:03.705 --> 00:19:06.993
We know we're out of time.

00:19:32.215 --> 00:19:32.500
He knows where the American economy is.

00:19:32.500 --> 00:19:37.058
But I said, "Watch what happens when he attacks Iran and attacks this area over there.

00:19:41.943 --> 00:19:42.314
" It's going to happen.

00:19:42.314 --> 00:19:53.525
Remember, I said, "He'll go after Venezuela and he'll get Venezuela and then he's going to go after Iran.

00:19:54.095 --> 00:19:54.665
" And guess what?

00:19:58.646 --> 00:19:58.897
It happened exactly the way the Lord said.

00:19:58.897 --> 00:20:12.840
You can go look through all the videos of every time the Lord warned us about it.

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:21.400
And I said, "Then he will say, drill, baby, drill.

00:20:21.400 --> 00:20:23.480
" And he did.

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:41.747
We will take Iran back to the Stone Age and they will.

00:20:41.747 --> 00:20:57.703
When this takes place, I said people will start to buy oil from America and it will make America's economy booming again and it will look like everybody and their brother is coming to America to buy oil.

00:20:57.703 --> 00:21:05.617
Does anybody remember this stuff that I'm telling you?

00:21:05.617 --> 00:21:13.206
I said it will stimulate and there'll be oil all in the Gulf of America.

00:21:13.206 --> 00:21:17.180
There'll be oil coming out of Houston.

00:21:17.180 --> 00:21:27.594
I saw pipelines being opened up and they'll start to talk about reestablishing major pipelines and oil will flow from Canada.

00:21:35.700 --> 00:21:35.912
I saw all this oil going on and a greater stronger economy and all these things.

00:21:35.912 --> 00:21:37.285
Today, look what they say.

00:21:37.285 --> 00:21:39.660
Look, the Strait has been closed again.

00:21:39.660 --> 00:21:41.160
I don't know.

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:46.411
I think it was by America; we closed it.

00:22:02.520 --> 00:22:03.398
You aren't going to go down that anymore because of the agreement.

00:22:04.276 --> 00:22:17.020
The US military says it will start a blockade of all ships going to and from Iran on Monday.

00:22:17.020 --> 00:22:19.331
No more oil for you.

00:22:19.331 --> 00:22:20.909
What did I say?

00:22:20.909 --> 00:22:22.898
What did the Lord say?

00:22:22.898 --> 00:22:23.876
It's not me.

00:22:23.876 --> 00:22:27.408
Even on my best day, I can't.

00:22:27.408 --> 00:22:31.280
What did the Lord say?

00:22:36.183 --> 00:22:39.467
The US military says it will start a blockade of all shipping going to and from Iran on Monday.

00:22:39.467 --> 00:22:45.120
So, how long will that happen?

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:47.737
Well, where are they going to go?

00:22:47.737 --> 00:22:51.540
Look, Braden, show them where they're going.

00:22:51.540 --> 00:22:54.720
Where are all these boats headed?

00:22:54.720 --> 00:22:55.350
Right here.

00:22:55.350 --> 00:22:56.400
Look at the boats.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:57.444
This is real time.

00:22:57.444 --> 00:23:00.114
This isn't the Strait of Hormuz.

00:23:00.114 --> 00:23:01.051
This is America.

00:23:01.051 --> 00:23:02.777
Look, can you show them?

00:23:02.777 --> 00:23:05.160
You're blocking it.

00:23:05.160 --> 00:23:07.547
Look at all those boats coming out of there.

00:23:07.809 --> 00:23:10.380
And then I said, "Watch what we do with Panama.

00:23:10.380 --> 00:23:23.920
" Remember I said the Lord said we are going to establish ourselves very strong in the Panama Canal and we will have great oil coming out of Houston, out of this area, out of the Gulf.

00:23:26.440 --> 00:23:27.507
And I said, "Watch drill, baby, drill.

00:23:27.507 --> 00:23:30.520
" Look at all those boats.

00:23:30.520 --> 00:23:33.960
They're all coming here to get our oil.

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:36.680
