' I believe in my heart.

00:49:57.769 --> 00:50:03.510
Did you know that prophet so-and-so said this?

00:50:03.510 --> 00:50:08.732
Did you know that prophet so-and-so?

00:50:18.159 --> 00:50:18.678
I don't listen to prophet so-and-so; I listen to Jesus.

00:50:19.716 --> 00:50:23.200
I don't care what prophet so-and-so said.

00:50:34.760 --> 00:50:35.708
I'm not accountable for what prophet so-and-so said; I'm only accountable for what He's told me.

00:50:35.708 --> 00:50:45.432
So, I don't care what this one said over there and that one said over there.

00:50:45.432 --> 00:50:56.635
You know what the Bible says also: that there will be many false prophets in the last days.

00:50:56.635 --> 00:50:59.288
So be careful who you're listening to.

00:50:59.584 --> 00:51:07.120
If you want to say I'm a false prophet because I'm telling people to get saved and Jesus is coming...

00:51:08.992 --> 00:51:13.680
and the Lord said, 'Be a John the Baptist in these last days.

00:51:13.680 --> 00:51:15.578
Tell people I'm coming, Brandon.

00:51:15.578 --> 00:51:19.968
They're running out of time.

00:51:19.968 --> 00:51:39.794
' And if I tell you that with all my heart and you call me a false prophet and Jesus shows up, I'm going to sit there and go, 'Well, at least we tried.

00:51:39.794 --> 00:51:44.750
' My heart is the harvest.

00:51:44.750 --> 00:51:53.086
My heart is to bring as many of you all with me as I can to tell you that Jesus Christ loves you and He has a plan for your life.

00:51:54.560 --> 00:52:00.985
And it's to bless you and not to harm you, so that you will have a great and expected end, that you have healing in your body if you would receive it.

00:52:03.280 --> 00:52:18.010
That Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever, and He is a healer and He is a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:52:33.560 --> 00:52:33.856
So call me a false prophet, call me somebody that's off, but I'm going to tell you that Jesus loves you and I pray for you and I pray you know Him.

00:52:33.856 --> 00:52:40.440
Nothing else matters other than: do you have a relationship with Jesus Christ?

00:52:40.440 --> 00:52:45.858
If you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity?

00:52:45.858 --> 00:52:53.920
All the things that are happening all around us and the acceleration of what the Lord told us was coming—it's happening.

00:52:53.920 --> 00:52:59.100
So if this is happening, is your heart ready for the coming of the Lord?

00:53:08.245 --> 00:53:08.600
He said, 'I'm coming.

00:53:08.600 --> 00:53:11.910
I'm standing at the door.

00:53:11.910 --> 00:53:19.000
' This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:53:19.000 --> 00:53:21.960
Brandon, the sun is setting on this timeframe.

00:53:21.960 --> 00:53:23.285
Whether that's five years...

00:53:32.429 --> 00:53:36.484
I had one man ask, 'Well, can you tell me if it's 3 years, 5 years, or 10 years?

00:53:36.484 --> 00:53:37.704
What do you believe?

00:53:37.704 --> 00:53:38.977
' I don't know.

00:53:38.977 --> 00:53:44.968
No man knows the day or the hour the Son of Man comes.

00:53:44.968 --> 00:53:46.116
That's what the Bible says.

00:53:46.116 --> 00:53:53.176
But we know the signs as we watch the fig tree.

00:53:53.176 --> 00:53:58.044
We know the signs as we watch the things that are happening all around us.

00:54:20.707 --> 00:54:21.249
And I'm going to tell you, as a frog in the pot, many of you are being boiled and you don't even realize it yet.

00:54:21.249 --> 00:54:47.992
You have your head in the sand and you see the birthing pains all around you with the weather and the major droughts and the wars and the rumors of wars and the pestilence and the plagues that are coming and the five shakings the Lord told us was coming with our president.

00:54:47.992 --> 00:54:52.240
He said, 'President Trump won't make this if you don't pray for him.

00:54:52.240 --> 00:54:54.484
He won't make it until January 2029.

00:54:54.484 --> 00:54:55.596
He'll never make it.

00:54:55.596 --> 00:54:56.040
Why?

00:54:56.040 --> 00:55:03.000
Because he can't do this alone.

00:55:03.000 --> 00:55:05.526
He must have us pray for him.

00:55:05.526 --> 00:55:11.160
' Do you believe he's a puppet to Israel?

00:55:11.160 --> 00:55:16.333
There are so many people saying, 'Israel and Benjamin is a bad man.

00:55:16.333 --> 00:55:24.869
' Listen, I told you I don't always agree with the Israeli government, but I always stand with Israel because Israel is forever.

00:55:24.869 --> 00:55:28.787
Do I agree with the United States government?

00:55:28.787 --> 00:55:33.984
Do I agree with everything President Trump says when he says bad words?

00:55:33.984 --> 00:55:34.688
No.

00:55:34.688 --> 00:55:53.544
But I pray for him with all my heart that God will give him a Road to Damascus experience and that it would shake him in the midnight hour and that he would have a glorious experience with my Heavenly Father.

00:55:53.544 --> 00:56:04.400
Because the only thing that's going to save America is not President Trump; it is an awakening unto God.

00:56:21.800 --> 00:56:29.154
I don't care if President Trump came out tomorrow and was speaking in tongues on camera and Paula White's up there praying in tongues next to him, and you got my other friends up there praying and you see Don up there busting out in tongues and everybody's shouting, 'Fire on you!

00:56:29.154 --> 00:56:38.320
' and people are falling out all over the place—which I believe could happen—but even then, it will not save America.

00:56:38.320 --> 00:57:04.498
The only thing that's going to save America is an awakening unto God and for God to pour out His Spirit upon this nation one more time, and the preachers preaching repentance and holiness back in the pulpits and telling the people that you must live right and act right and stop living a compromising life because they're going to hell.

00:57:13.800 --> 00:57:14.080
And tell them the truth.

00:57:16.760 --> 00:57:16.960
It's time to wake up.

00:57:16.960 --> 00:57:23.690
It's time to tell the people that Jesus is coming and you must get your heart right.

00:57:23.690 --> 00:57:30.476
But there's so many people that want to play pat-a-cake Christianity.

00:57:30.476 --> 00:57:38.760
And if you don't say something certain right on social media, which is trash in the first place, they go, 'Well, you're anti-Semite!

00:57:38.760 --> 00:57:39.640
You're this!

00:57:39.640 --> 00:57:40.520
You're that!

00:57:40.520 --> 00:57:45.920
' And I go, 'No, I'm not.

00:57:49.484 --> 00:57:49.747
I love the Jews more than anybody.

00:57:50.271 --> 00:57:51.058
I pray for them.

00:57:51.058 --> 00:57:54.036
I pray for the people.

00:57:54.604 --> 00:58:05.496
Just because I don't always agree with some of the government decisions, just like I don't agree with a lot of the things that we do, doesn't mean I'm anti-Semitism.

00:58:05.496 --> 00:58:09.731
' You don't have to be mean to people you don't agree with.

00:58:10.023 --> 00:58:12.017
You can be nice to folks.

00:58:12.017 --> 00:58:16.500
Who are we always to be throwing rocks at folks?

00:58:16.500 --> 00:58:21.366
Show love to folks, whatever tribe or tongue you are.

00:58:21.366 --> 00:58:30.570
Let's just say that Jesus loves you and it's time to repent and turn to Him before it's too late.

00:58:44.147 --> 00:58:44.373
I don't know, I just see so much hate.

00:58:44.373 --> 00:58:52.900
There's so much hate in emails where people say, 'You said this, you said that.

00:58:52.900 --> 00:58:55.220
' My goodness, anybody can twist anything you say.

00:58:58.280 --> 00:59:02.080
And when I talk as much as I do for two and a half hours, I say a lot of stuff.

00:59:13.097 --> 00:59:13.429
And you do that times five when I do these videos.

00:59:13.429 --> 00:59:16.040
At the end of the week, I'm tired.

00:59:17.890 --> 00:59:18.490
I have to have a couple days off just to refocus.

00:59:30.220 --> 00:59:31.507
I don't want to miss Him in my own personal life, always trying to hear Him and put out what the Lord is saying for me to say to you so that you all don't miss it.

00:59:33.302 --> 00:59:34.280
I don't want to miss it.

00:59:34.616 --> 00:59:43.724
I have some big decisions to make, huge, more than I can ever convey on this platform or ever tell you what's going on in my personal life right now.

00:59:43.724 --> 00:59:47.730
But it is what it is.

00:59:47.730 --> 00:59:50.831
We count it all joy.

00:59:56.540 --> 01:00:00.124
I was asking Him about what I told you last time about the greater glory and about plateauing in ministry.

01:00:01.880 --> 01:00:09.404
I woke up one morning and I was sitting there and He said, 'I already told you in my Word.

01:00:09.404 --> 01:00:13.020
How do you get the greater glory?

01:00:13.020 --> 01:00:21.650
You've asked this in your heart and you even said it on your platform.

01:00:21.650 --> 01:00:24.720
' He said, 'It's Refiner's Fire.

01:00:24.720 --> 01:00:35.600
If you want to go to the greater glory, it comes through refining.

01:00:50.147 --> 01:00:50.573
The reason plateaus happen and you're not going from glory to glory is because you've limited Me and how I'm able to refine you.

01:00:50.573 --> 01:00:55.473
' I've had enough; I don't want any more refining.

01:00:55.473 --> 01:01:03.194
He said, 'But Brandon, My heart is for you to go from glory to glory.

01:01:03.194 --> 01:01:16.840
' He's changing me into His likeness and image to perfect in me the love of God shown to the world.

01:01:16.840 --> 01:01:22.501
For He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:01:22.501 --> 01:01:39.663
He's changing you into His likeness and image to perfect in you the love of God shown to the world from glory to glory.

01:01:39.663 --> 01:02:02.510
Many people, when they get to a certain level, like I saw with an old pastor—he wanted 10,000 members so bad, he had a goal of 10,000 members, and for the 13-plus years that we worked there, we never achieved it; we made it to 8,500.

01:02:02.510 --> 01:02:06.040
We made it to 85.

01:02:06.040 --> 01:02:10.064
Some Easter Sundays we would bust 15.

01:02:10.064 --> 01:02:16.540
But his whole goal was to get to a certain amount.

01:02:16.540 --> 01:02:17.690
It was his focus.

01:02:26.680 --> 01:02:27.040
And the Lord started showing me.

01:02:30.909 --> 01:02:31.286
He said, "If your focus is that, you're missing it.

01:02:31.286 --> 01:02:33.782
Outward growth for man's approval—you're missing it.

01:02:33.782 --> 01:02:39.760
Growth should always be to impact my kingdom, from glory to glory, for the souls, for healings, and demonstration.

01:02:39.760 --> 01:02:45.490
But if it's ever just for ego—if it ever comes about just being for ego—I'll never allow it.

01:02:45.490 --> 01:02:46.178
Ego is a destroyer.

01:02:46.178 --> 01:02:52.634
" So many times I've—like even with this last blessed brother—he showed me his church this weekend.

01:02:52.634 --> 01:02:59.365
He said, "I want you to come here and I'll help you get a home.

01:02:59.365 --> 01:03:00.800
I'll do all these things.

01:03:00.800 --> 01:03:08.160
" One of the largest churches in America offered me finances to bless my family, big money to help us.

01:03:10.070 --> 01:03:10.260
And I was like, "This is God, Lord.

01:03:10.260 --> 01:03:10.450
This is you.

01:03:10.450 --> 01:03:13.485
It has to be you.

01:03:13.485 --> 01:03:22.533
" But the Lord said to me, "Are you going to deliberately disobey what I've asked you to do?

01:03:33.434 --> 01:03:33.669
" I said, "What do you mean?

01:03:33.669 --> 01:03:35.260
Any blessings from you, right?

01:03:35.260 --> 01:03:37.336
Any open door has to be from you.

01:03:37.336 --> 01:03:43.840
" He said, "No, I told you to sit on the back row and pray at this little church.

01:03:45.947 --> 01:03:47.960
" You know, I realize that maybe my character can't handle that yet.

01:03:47.960 --> 01:03:51.600
Maybe my character can't handle a church with 40,000 or 50,000 people.

01:03:51.600 --> 01:03:56.605
Maybe I can do this behind a camera because I don't see you face to face.

01:03:57.460 --> 01:03:57.745
I don't know.

01:03:57.745 --> 01:04:00.171
What is God protecting me from?

01:04:00.171 --> 01:04:01.126
From myself.

01:04:09.608 --> 01:04:10.568
I could go anywhere in any church because I've been offered it so many times, but every single time it's always to a little congregation with just several hundred people.

01:04:10.568 --> 01:04:12.611
Sit on the back row.

01:04:12.611 --> 01:04:13.780
Humble yourself.

01:04:13.780 --> 01:04:20.823
And I think it's very interesting because the same said, "Don't forget the janitor.

01:04:20.823 --> 01:04:25.116
I'll make you a household name throughout this for me, not for you.

01:04:25.116 --> 01:04:32.440
I'll not share my glory with you at all, but you can speak for me.

01:04:33.280 --> 01:04:37.800
And I allow you to give these words and they'll prove to be accurate.

01:04:37.800 --> 01:04:41.787
But anytime you ever get a big head about it, it's taken that fast.

01:04:41.787 --> 01:04:46.980
You're just a glove and the Holy Spirit fills the glove and he makes the glove operate.

01:04:47.280 --> 01:04:49.058
You can do nothing apart from me.

01:04:52.314 --> 01:04:56.640
The glove only has life when I put my hand in it.

01:04:58.669 --> 01:04:58.971
You don't control the gift.

01:04:58.971 --> 01:04:59.880
I do.

01:05:13.747 --> 01:05:14.053
Don't ever forget that.

01:05:14.053 --> 01:05:20.210
" And so many of you think, "Well, I'm going to go and do this.

01:05:30.267 --> 01:05:30.418
I'm going to do that.

01:05:37.653 --> 01:05:37.836
" Not without me.

01:05:37.836 --> 01:05:41.743
As I sit and I look at my flowers, I realize...

01:05:43.290 --> 01:05:47.285
I sit out and I just look at them and let the sun just hit my face.

01:05:47.285 --> 01:05:53.470
I sit there and I realize in that stillness, Brandon probably doesn't have the character to handle that yet.

01:05:53.470 --> 01:05:54.485
I'm not dead enough.

01:05:54.485 --> 01:05:56.480
But he allowed me to do this.

01:05:57.320 --> 01:05:59.320
And I don't ever want anything to jeopardize my relationship with him.

01:05:59.320 --> 01:06:02.160
This is just a byproduct of something that I've spent years cultivating.

01:06:02.160 --> 01:06:05.093
I've listened and I listen and I stay at his feet.

01:06:05.093 --> 01:06:17.751
But if money, if fame, if all this can destroy me and take me to nothing and cost me my marriage, who cares?

01:06:17.751 --> 01:06:21.930
If you can gain the whole world and lose your soul...

01:06:21.930 --> 01:06:28.160
they may have the character to handle it because God gave it to them, but it doesn't mean you are.

01:06:28.160 --> 01:06:30.971
It doesn't mean you're ready.

01:06:30.971 --> 01:06:44.620
Maybe there's something in you the Lord sees, and he says, "You're not ready for that yet, but I'll allow you to be used at this level because I need you right now.

01:06:44.620 --> 01:07:15.345
" I remember sitting out in a Homeland parking lot in Guthrie, Oklahoma—and it was before it was a Savers—and the Lord told me, he said, "I want to use you for the ministry, and you're going to bring healing to the nations like Oral Roberts, and all these things are going to happen with you.

01:07:20.680 --> 01:07:22.480
" And I remember sitting there and I said, "Lord, if you're going to do it, then just do it.

01:07:22.480 --> 01:07:29.000
I'm tired of waiting and hearing you tell me about that.

01:07:29.000 --> 01:07:36.240
" And boy, I tell you what, that was a really stupid thing to say.

01:07:38.400 --> 01:07:40.313
We get impatient and we want everything to be microwaved.

01:07:40.313 --> 01:07:43.540
But to go from glory to glory takes character.

01:07:47.320 --> 01:07:52.276
And it takes you being stripped away from your pride because he doesn't want to lose you—to gain the whole world and lose your soul.

01:07:52.276 --> 01:08:00.695
So if God wants you just to pray on a YouTube channel of mine, thank you for being here.

01:08:00.695 --> 01:08:02.060
Thank you.

01:08:04.210 --> 01:08:05.200
For many hands make light work.

01:08:08.080 --> 01:08:12.160
And I believe the best is yet to come for every single one of us.

01:08:14.537 --> 01:08:26.427
And we have a part just like this guy praying for Finney—praying for the people down in Miami, praying for those that go and say, "We had 40,000 people, we had this, we had that.

01:08:26.427 --> 01:08:27.440
" Praise God, man.

01:08:27.440 --> 01:08:31.759
Obviously, if God thought I could handle it, he would give it to me.

01:08:31.759 --> 01:08:36.782
But until then, "Obey me for what I've asked you to do.

01:08:37.815 --> 01:08:50.255
" And sometimes you can have everything offered to you and everything under the sun being presented to you and the Lord says, "Don't touch it.

01:08:50.255 --> 01:08:52.100
" Maybe he will tomorrow.

01:08:52.100 --> 01:08:53.420
I don't know.

01:08:53.420 --> 01:08:56.103
All I know is right now.

01:08:56.103 --> 01:08:57.331
He said no.

01:09:00.751 --> 01:09:01.067
And I get so disappointed.

01:09:15.160 --> 01:09:15.420
I walk away angry about it sometimes.

01:09:15.420 --> 01:09:16.720
I go, "Why me?

01:09:16.720 --> 01:09:18.796
" kicking a rock like a little kid.

01:09:35.920 --> 01:09:36.170
I get in the car.

01:09:43.395 --> 01:09:43.630
I drive around for a little bit and pray.

01:09:43.630 --> 01:09:44.335
Diana goes...

01:09:44.335 --> 01:09:50.600
I told her today, I said, "Thank God you've put up with me all these years.

01:09:59.457 --> 01:09:59.760
You've stood by my side even when I act like a little brat, cranky about something stupid.

01:10:08.170 --> 01:10:08.505
I want to do this.

01:10:19.390 --> 01:10:20.540
I want to do that.

01:10:27.960 --> 01:10:28.600
" But I don't want to ever lose the ability to hear him like I do.

01:10:28.600 --> 01:10:32.154
When he comes and visits...

01:10:32.154 --> 01:10:42.777
he'll come and visit and he'll sit down and we'll talk, and the Holy Spirit is so real and the presence of the Lord fills my whole house.

01:10:43.680 --> 01:10:48.680
And I'll be able to see over into the other side—angels in heaven and beautiful things.

01:10:48.680 --> 01:10:53.571
But if you were to gain the whole world and lose that, who cares?

01:10:53.571 --> 01:10:55.429
There's something that I...

01:10:55.429 --> 01:11:06.280
this is worth more to me: to have a relationship with him and know what's coming and warn the people as much as I can.

01:11:06.280 --> 01:11:07.480
The ones that will listen.

01:11:08.258 --> 01:11:25.335
And live by myself—be by myself, you know, with hardly any friends or whatever—and just be following the Holy Ghost and just say, "Hey, at least I know that all my family—my mom, my dad, my brothers, my sisters—are all serving the Lord.

01:11:25.335 --> 01:11:27.490
We all love the Lord.

01:11:27.490 --> 01:11:31.870
We all are baptized in the Holy Ghost.

01:11:31.870 --> 01:11:33.575
We pray in tongues, casting out devils.

01:11:37.289 --> 01:11:37.418
" You have to believe, hey, that stands for a lot.

01:11:37.418 --> 01:11:47.760
Regardless if your name is known throughout the whole world and you're having a huge auditorium full of people and everybody's clapping and saying whatever.

01:11:47.760 --> 01:11:49.360
People's opinions change.

01:11:49.360 --> 01:11:53.930
I've seen it on this internet and it is toxic.

01:11:53.930 --> 01:11:59.418
Does that make sense what I'm trying to tell y'all?

01:11:59.418 --> 01:12:07.143
I try to present my life and what I'm learning just by things that I see, because I see so much.

01:12:07.143 --> 01:12:15.509
And I want you to really search your heart tonight and really know him.

01:12:15.509 --> 01:12:21.829
And it's not in all the hype.

01:12:23.889 --> 01:12:24.031
He's in that still small voice.

01:12:25.044 --> 01:12:25.156
He's not in the lights.

01:12:25.156 --> 01:12:26.234
He's not in the spotlight.

01:12:26.234 --> 01:12:27.900
He's not in all the junk.

01:12:27.900 --> 01:12:30.569
He's in that still small voice inside of you.

01:12:31.080 --> 01:12:35.735
And when you get real—oh God—and you crucify yourself, crucify your flesh daily.

01:12:40.069 --> 01:12:40.314
I die daily.

01:12:42.804 --> 01:12:43.009
I die daily.

01:12:50.240 --> 01:12:50.440
What is it that keeps you dead?

01:12:54.110 --> 01:12:54.405
Don't resurrect the old man.

01:12:55.290 --> 01:12:55.880
What keeps you dead?

01:12:55.880 --> 01:13:01.750
So that you are crucified with Christ; nevertheless, Christ in me, the hope of glory.

01:13:04.800 --> 01:13:12.760
I am so sold out to him that in these last days when he says, "Go and do this, do that," I want to be obedient.

01:13:12.760 --> 01:13:15.160
Quickly obey.

01:13:15.160 --> 01:13:15.865
Quickly obey.

01:13:15.865 --> 01:13:20.810
Whatever he says for you to do, do it.

01:13:20.810 --> 01:13:29.280
So if you're here tonight and you say, "Brandon, I just wish you could pray for me.

01:13:29.280 --> 01:13:34.743
Could you pray for me?

01:13:41.060 --> 01:13:41.320
I'm not right with the Lord.

01:13:44.071 --> 01:13:50.622
You say all of these things and I feel inside of myself, man, I have so far to go.

01:13:50.622 --> 01:13:51.600
" We all do.

01:13:51.600 --> 01:13:53.551
We're all a work in progress.

01:13:53.551 --> 01:13:56.451
None of us have perfected any of this.

01:13:56.451 --> 01:14:09.632
But I'm going to tell you, if you're not even in the door yet, and you're standing on the outside looking in, it's time for you to give your heart to Jesus Christ tonight.

01:14:09.632 --> 01:14:27.460
Before we take any further prayer or whatever, I want you to really become real with God right now and just say, "I don't know if I was to die tonight where I would spend eternity, Brandon.

01:14:27.460 --> 01:14:28.200
" I really don't.

01:14:28.200 --> 01:14:44.480
If you have any kind of question in your heart at all, why go any further until you know that if you died tonight, you'd know where you'll spend eternity?

01:14:53.863 --> 01:14:54.651
I want to pray for you.

01:14:57.991 --> 01:14:59.044
I want you to get real with yourself right now.

01:15:01.445 --> 01:15:01.660
