01:15:18.571 --> 01:15:20.950
You've got that inward tugging.

01:15:22.900 --> 01:15:28.716
The Holy Spirit's just screaming on the inside of you, 'You're going the wrong way.

01:15:28.716 --> 01:15:40.629
