01:23:16.128 --> 01:23:16.592
I ask you to wash me, make me clean tonight.

01:24:02.480 --> 01:24:04.187
I turn my back on the world.

01:24:28.720 --> 01:24:29.257
I turn my back on the devil.

01:24:32.480 --> 01:24:33.485
I turn my back on my sin.

01:24:33.485 --> 01:24:37.625
Jesus, I repent of all my sins.

01:24:37.980 --> 01:24:40.696
I repent of them all.

01:24:48.040 --> 01:24:48.336
I shouldn't have been doing it.

01:24:48.928 --> 01:24:50.704
I ask you to forgive me.

01:24:50.704 --> 01:24:52.307
Forgive me, Lord.

01:24:52.307 --> 01:25:07.302
You said to confess my sins, that you are faithful and just to forgive me of my sins and cleanse me of all unrighteousness.

01:25:08.404 --> 01:25:13.200
And so I confess those sins before you right now.

01:25:13.200 --> 01:25:21.720
Jesus, I thank you that from this day forward, I belong to you.

01:25:21.720 --> 01:25:29.253
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:25:29.876 --> 01:25:33.290
I dedicate my all, my heart, my everything to you.

01:25:33.290 --> 01:25:38.960
Tonight's my night.

01:25:46.960 --> 01:25:47.345
I want to be born again tonight.

01:25:47.345 --> 01:25:48.885
Tonight's my night.

01:25:48.885 --> 01:25:57.700
I'll serve you with everything I have.

01:25:57.700 --> 01:26:08.943
Thank you, Lord, that I am forgiven.

01:26:08.943 --> 01:26:21.775
Thank you, Lord, that you are my Savior now and forever.

01:27:12.520 --> 01:27:12.850
I believe with all my heart that you have forgiven me and that you are the Son of God.

01:27:12.850 --> 01:27:18.006
Thank you, Lord, that today is a fresh, clean start.

01:27:18.480 --> 01:27:21.000
I say it with all my heart.

01:27:40.000 --> 01:27:40.274
I'm yours and you're mine, and I'll serve you from this day forward.

01:28:12.406 --> 01:28:12.743
And if I were to die tonight, Lord, I know now where I'll go.

01:28:12.743 --> 01:28:14.960
I'll be with you in paradise forever.

01:28:14.960 --> 01:28:16.496
Thank you, Lord.

01:28:16.496 --> 01:28:20.040
Thank you, Jesus, for dying for me.

01:28:20.040 --> 01:28:21.624
Amen and amen.

01:28:21.624 --> 01:29:09.460
' I believe that if you just said that simple prayer, you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ and he said, 'Behold, I make all things new tonight.

01:29:09.460 --> 01:29:11.327
' Tonight's your fresh, clean start.

01:29:11.327 --> 01:29:14.340
Tonight is a brand new start for you.

01:29:14.340 --> 01:29:17.611
Now, what do you do?

01:29:17.611 --> 01:29:19.149
Find a Bible-believing church.

01:29:19.149 --> 01:29:24.693
That's where I would go—to a Bible-believing church, a non-denominational church.

01:29:24.693 --> 01:29:35.447
Get plugged in there.

01:29:35.447 --> 01:29:42.030
Get radical about your decision today.

01:29:42.030 --> 01:29:46.491
Tell all your friends and family, 'I just accepted Jesus Christ.

01:29:46.491 --> 01:30:15.160
He is my Lord and Savior, and you need to make him your Lord and Savior, too.

01:30:15.160 --> 01:30:21.804
' And they may say, 'I don't want anything to do with that,' or whatever.

01:30:21.804 --> 01:30:23.410
Hey, you know what?

01:30:23.410 --> 01:30:25.000
That's okay.

01:30:25.000 --> 01:30:27.680
I'll keep praying for you.

01:30:27.680 --> 01:31:20.710
If they say, 'Come on, let's go party,' no, we're not going to go party.

01:31:20.710 --> 01:31:23.840
'I'm going to go to church.

01:31:24.560 --> 01:31:27.072
You want to come with me?

01:31:27.072 --> 01:31:29.208
' 'No.

01:31:29.208 --> 01:31:32.680
' 'Okay, well then suit yourself.

01:31:52.280 --> 01:31:52.460
I'm going to church.

01:31:52.460 --> 01:31:59.790
' And eventually, you'll find new friends or they'll come eventually and be a part of it.

01:31:59.790 --> 01:32:06.347
But they're going to see that there's something different inside of you.

01:32:06.676 --> 01:32:07.662
And that's Jesus.

01:32:07.662 --> 01:32:09.760
You're wall-to-wall Holy Ghost now.

01:32:09.760 --> 01:32:36.107
Now, what you're going to do is read your Bible, pray, and go to that pastor and say, 'Listen, I need to be water baptized.

01:32:36.107 --> 01:32:39.984
Will you help me?

01:32:39.984 --> 01:32:41.444
' Get water baptized.

01:32:42.028 --> 01:33:09.312
Get plugged in on Sundays, Wednesdays, whatever they've got going on.

01:33:09.312 --> 01:33:42.600
Get excited about your decision tonight that you gave your heart to Jesus Christ.

01:33:42.600 --> 01:34:12.990
If you can't afford a Bible and you just gave your heart to the Lord and you say, 'Brandon, could you help me get a Bible?

01:34:16.920 --> 01:34:27.933
' I will give you a Bible absolutely for free.

01:34:27.933 --> 01:34:36.048
My wife and I will send it to you just to be a blessing.

01:34:36.048 --> 01:34:36.872
You just email us in the description below.

01:34:36.872 --> 01:34:38.255
If there's an email address there, say, 'Listen, I just got born again.

01:34:38.255 --> 01:34:38.996
Can you help me get a Bible?

01:34:38.996 --> 01:34:39.796
' We'll send you one, no questions asked.

01:34:39.796 --> 01:34:40.446
We're not going to solicit you.

01:34:40.446 --> 01:34:41.515
We just want to tell you: Welcome to the family.

01:34:41.515 --> 01:34:41.752
Welcome home.

01:34:59.280 --> 01:35:01.180
But what I will ask you to do is like, subscribe, click the notification bell, be a part of this YouTube channel, and come here and pray with us every single time we're live.

01:35:01.180 --> 01:35:13.920
We try to go live at least five times a week.

01:35:24.308 --> 01:35:24.440
I just want to let you know we love you and we're excited you're here.

01:35:24.440 --> 01:35:37.240
All 64 of you that gave your heart to Jesus Christ tonight, welcome to the family.

01:35:37.240 --> 01:35:40.792
All heaven is rejoicing.

01:36:53.520 --> 01:37:09.314
The angels are rejoicing for all 64 of you.

01:37:11.680 --> 01:37:16.373
And hell is saying, 'Man, we just lost a great sinner tonight.

01:37:16.373 --> 01:37:38.648
' And they're very bummed out because they just lost a good sinner.

01:37:41.660 --> 01:37:48.336
And I believe the best is yet to come for you.

01:37:48.336 --> 01:38:14.130
Now, if you fall down and skin your knee through sin or whatever, you run to God; you don't run from him.

01:38:14.130 --> 01:38:48.030
You run to him with all your heart, and your sin now is none of the devil's business.

01:38:48.040 --> 01:38:51.080
Say, 'Listen, I messed up today, Lord.

01:38:51.080 --> 01:39:24.140
' He's like, 'Yeah, I know it, but the moment you confess it, it's okay.

01:39:24.140 --> 01:39:32.102
' Just keep going after him with your whole heart; he will change you from the inside out.

01:39:32.102 --> 01:39:43.076
Now, a toddler falls and they mess up.

01:39:43.076 --> 01:42:41.667
As you grow up to be an adult, you don't fall as much anymore because you're good at walking once you've got your walk down.

01:42:51.360 --> 01:42:51.859
But for a baby, there's a lot of grace.

01:42:51.859 --> 01:42:58.190
Look at what happens: a little toddler falls down, they just fall.

01:42:58.190 --> 01:43:17.391
But even an adult, when they fall, God's not up there beating them with a stick saying, 'I'm mad at you.

01:43:17.391 --> 01:43:18.989
' But you'll grow.

01:43:25.760 --> 01:43:25.975
The word is going to change you from the inside out.

01:43:27.265 --> 01:43:30.280
And those things that used to bother you are not going to bother you very much anymore.

01:43:30.280 --> 01:43:32.617
Watch.

01:43:52.393 --> 01:43:52.920
Because the Bible's going to change you and you're going to go, 'Man, I feel different.

01:43:57.840 --> 01:43:58.840
I used to be so addicted to this stuff.

01:43:58.840 --> 01:44:14.040
' And the more you change, the Bible says that you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

01:44:14.040 --> 01:44:23.280
So tonight, you have to get that word down inside of your heart.

01:44:23.280 --> 01:44:29.102
That's the only way you're going to stay free.

01:44:34.360 --> 01:44:39.360
And the more you get it down inside of you, you're not going to be attracted to the things you used to be anymore.

01:44:39.360 --> 01:44:45.298
You're going to go, 'You know what?

01:44:45.298 --> 01:44:49.897
That doesn't even seem like—why did I used to do that?

01:44:49.897 --> 01:44:57.840
' because the Bible's going to change you, the Word of God.

01:44:57.840 --> 01:44:59.331
So, praise the Lord.

01:44:59.331 --> 01:45:00.566
All right.

01:45:00.566 --> 01:45:13.200
Who wants to take communion with me and pray now for all 64 of you?

01:45:13.200 --> 01:45:15.016
That's wonderful, Braden.

01:45:18.680 --> 01:45:19.000
A good start of the week.

