Push him over there.

01:46:05.720 --> 01:46:12.870
You just had him on there, son.

01:46:12.880 --> 01:46:13.930
Right there.

01:46:13.930 --> 01:46:14.980
There's Mike.

01:46:14.980 --> 01:46:17.570
We're praying for Mike.

01:46:17.570 --> 01:46:19.800
Go ahead and play Mike.

01:46:19.800 --> 01:46:25.140
This is who we've been praying for: Mike Lindell.

01:46:25.140 --> 01:46:26.480
'Hello everybody.

