It's pretty early.

01:46:35.680 --> 01:46:45.977
It's getting a little rain, and we're heading into an event here for a governor's race.

01:46:45.977 --> 01:46:49.720
Then we're going to head from here to Minneapolis.

01:46:49.720 --> 01:46:54.165
We're doing two in one day today, right in downtown Minneapolis.

01:46:54.165 --> 01:46:56.587
It should be a great day.

01:46:56.587 --> 01:47:00.270
' So we need to pray for him.

01:47:11.760 --> 01:47:12.129
I like his little bus.

01:47:12.129 --> 01:47:17.000
Father, we thank You, Lord, for godly people running for office.

01:47:17.000 --> 01:47:26.720
We thank You, Lord, that You keep them strong, Father, that they'll not get weary in well-doing.

01:47:26.720 --> 01:47:48.160
I thank You that they have plenty of funding, that his pillows are selling well, and his sheets, and all the stuff that he does.

01:47:48.160 --> 01:47:52.840
Lord, I ask You, God, that You give him wisdom on how to win this race.

01:48:19.520 --> 01:48:19.886
I pray for a turnaround in Minnesota.

01:48:19.886 --> 01:48:51.000
Even as we talk tonight, as we pray tonight, we're calling for a landslide victory and for the righteous people to rise up in Minnesota and win by a landslide.

01:48:51.000 --> 01:48:53.760
And it's not just about Minnesota, Lord.

01:48:53.760 --> 01:49:17.920
There'll be many leaders rising up in the midterms.

01:49:17.920 --> 01:49:23.880
And we give You glory, honor, and praise.

01:49:23.880 --> 01:49:37.010
Father, now we lift up this body and we thank You, Lord, that You took it all for us.

01:49:37.010 --> 01:49:49.440
Thank You, Lord, that we're crucified with Christ.

01:49:49.440 --> 01:50:03.540
Nevertheless, it's Christ in me, the hope of glory.

01:50:03.540 --> 01:50:08.450
I'm so thankful that You're in me.

01:50:08.450 --> 01:50:17.930
You dwell in me.

01:50:17.930 --> 01:50:35.435
You are my friend.

01:50:35.435 --> 01:50:47.513
And we take this body right now in the name of Jesus.

01:50:47.513 --> 01:51:40.875
And we thank You, Lord, that by Your stripes we are healed.

01:51:40.875 --> 01:52:21.740
You became sin, sickness, and poverty.

01:53:09.898 --> 01:53:13.024
You did it all for the whole man, that we could be whole in every area of our life: spirit, soul, and body.

01:53:23.560 --> 01:53:30.190
And we're so grateful, Father, in the name of Jesus for what You did for us.

01:53:47.783 --> 01:53:48.006
