01:53:48.006 --> 01:53:50.560
Lord, thank You for the blood.

01:53:50.560 --> 01:54:07.510
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:54:07.520 --> 01:54:13.707
We apply the blood over this week.

01:54:13.707 --> 01:54:19.820
We thank You, Lord, that this week will be victorious.

01:54:19.820 --> 01:54:42.840
I thank You, Father, that we make much of that blood right now from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

01:54:46.070 --> 01:55:06.520
The blood of Jesus covers us, the blood of Jesus covers me, the blood of Jesus covers my children—it covers us in the name of Jesus.

01:55:12.613 --> 01:55:12.916
And we thank You, Lord.

01:55:12.916 --> 01:55:28.760
I thank You, Father, that it never loses its power.

01:55:28.760 --> 01:55:39.920
Great is Your faithfulness to me, Lord.

01:55:39.920 --> 01:55:58.312
And I thank You, Father, that the best is yet to come.

01:55:58.312 --> 01:56:07.530
And we're going from glory to glory.

01:56:45.942 --> 01:56:46.200
And Father, we do it by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

01:56:46.200 --> 01:56:48.956
We put the devil under our feet.

01:57:02.240 --> 01:57:02.680
And Father, we're so grateful for all that You've done for us in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:57:19.640 --> 01:57:20.067
And we take this blood right now in Jesus' name, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:57:20.067 --> 01:57:25.840
I plead the blood over anything that You want to show me.

01:57:25.840 --> 01:57:31.560
Now, if You have anything to show us, we yield to You, Holy Spirit.

01:57:31.560 --> 01:57:35.160
And we, Father, jump right in that river.

01:57:35.160 --> 01:57:47.140
And I thank You, Father, that we pray for that which is to come.

01:57:47.140 --> 01:57:52.573
If You want to show us anything, fine.

01:57:52.573 --> 01:57:55.383
If not, that's all right, too.

01:57:55.383 --> 01:57:58.200
Father, we are just yielded over to You.

01:57:58.200 --> 01:58:10.960
Thank You, Lord, that we have eyes to see and we hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

01:58:10.960 --> 01:58:16.510
We take authority over hexes and vexes and curses of witchcraft of all kinds.

01:58:18.427 --> 01:58:20.273
And we say in the name of Jesus, it is under our feet.

01:58:20.273 --> 01:58:25.090
We pray for those that curse us, we bless those that try to come against us.

01:58:25.090 --> 01:58:37.034
We say in the name of Jesus, we bless you, and your words fall down and they will not prosper.

01:58:37.034 --> 01:58:44.710
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it in Jesus' name.

01:58:44.720 --> 01:58:47.520
And we thank You, Father, for it.

01:59:08.720 --> 01:59:09.126
And we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it.

01:59:09.126 --> 01:59:10.749
Amen and amen.

01:59:11.154 --> 01:59:12.560
You believe that?

01:59:12.560 --> 01:59:14.370
Take the blood.

01:59:14.370 --> 01:59:16.395
Every time it's different.

01:59:16.395 --> 01:59:20.833
That's why it's not religion; it's relationship.

01:59:20.833 --> 01:59:23.069
People go, 'Whoa.

01:59:23.069 --> 01:59:36.378
' If you knew how boring it would be if you said the same thing always to the Lord and you never had something fresh in there—it'd be just like a marriage.

01:59:36.378 --> 01:59:50.550
If you always say the same thing to your wife every single morning, every single day, all the time, she'll go, 'Is there any kind of originality to you at all in our marriage?

01:59:50.550 --> 01:59:59.126
' I'm sure after a while—after how many years—you're going to get bored with it, probably within a year.

01:59:59.126 --> 02:00:01.160
Make things fresh.

02:00:01.160 --> 02:00:07.920
Treat God like He's sitting right next to you.

02:00:12.484 --> 02:00:12.760
He has an opinion about everything and He'll teach you about everything.

02:00:12.760 --> 02:00:17.785
If you just get real with God, God will become real to you.

02:00:17.785 --> 02:00:20.680
Stop trying to hide and be so religious.

02:00:28.653 --> 02:00:28.867
Be just a friend.

02:00:28.867 --> 02:00:50.628
When you're a friend of God, strip yourself down of every preconceived idea of what you think God should be.

02:00:50.628 --> 02:00:56.704
Don't put God in a box anymore.

02:00:56.704 --> 02:01:00.120
'This is the way He's going to bless me.

02:01:00.120 --> 02:01:06.890
This is the way it's going to have to come.

02:01:06.890 --> 02:01:23.880
' If it doesn't come through crypto, if it doesn't come through this, then I guess I'm just—no.

02:01:23.880 --> 02:01:29.856
God has a million and one ways to bring it to you.

02:01:29.856 --> 02:01:33.875
Just trust Him for each one of them.

02:01:33.875 --> 02:02:28.740
You've got to stop putting God in a box.

02:02:28.740 --> 02:03:22.585
'Well, if it doesn't happen this way, it doesn't happen through my job, I guess I'm not going to be blessed anymore.

02:03:22.585 --> 02:03:49.785
If I don't get to be the vice president of McDonald's—if I work at McDonald's flipping burgers—if I'm not the vice president, I'm never going to be anything.

02:03:49.785 --> 02:03:55.696
' What if God wants you to be in another store?

02:04:04.415 --> 02:04:05.069
What if He has an idea for you?

02:04:05.069 --> 02:04:14.280
Don't limit God in what you think you should be doing.

02:04:14.280 --> 02:04:33.290
Let the Holy Spirit lead you and guide you, and He will shock and awe you.

02:04:37.366 --> 02:04:41.990
And you're going to go, 'I never saw that.

02:04:42.000 --> 02:05:15.630
' No eye has seen, nor ear heard, nor entered into the heart of man the things that God has in store for those that love Him.

02:05:16.547 --> 02:05:28.070
It's over and above all that you dare ask or think.

02:05:51.400 --> 02:05:51.695
He's exceedingly abundantly above all.

02:05:51.695 --> 02:05:54.160
That's the way I look at it.

02:05:54.160 --> 02:05:58.573
Father, we just thank You, Lord, for President Trump tonight.

02:06:16.063 --> 02:06:16.257
He needs some help.

02:06:16.257 --> 02:06:17.040
